description:
In this vastly popular talk, Fr. Gaitley describes the &quot;second greatest story ever told&quot; - a story that encompasses Divine Mercy, the life of Blessed Pope John Paul II, and the crucial role that Marian Consecration can play in your life. Fr. Michael Gaitley is a priest in the Congregation of Marian Fathers of the Immaculate Conception and the director of the Association of Marian Helpers, a spiritual benefit society with more than one million members. Be sure to also check out Fr. Gaitley's groundbreaking book on Marian consecration, 33 Days to Morning Glory.

